data.description: Opportunity knocks with this 1977 +/- sqft home sits on almost 1/3+/- acre property just outside town but still in a great neighborhood! This spacious home boasts a huge living room with a wood fireplace. Kitchen with great cabinet and counter space with an eating area and separate formal dining room. The primary bedroom with a large ensuite bath is conveniently located on the main level. A second family room downstairs for added versatility and 2 more bedrooms downstairs. Oversized yard with large patios in both back and front yard perfect for entertaining or relaxing while you bbq. While the home does need some attention with updates and repairs, the property holds incredible potential for your dream home!
